Hey, so unfortunately the open-source website that tracked private planes (even those that paid to be de-listed on public 
trackers, such as your target jet) is currently down as of just a couple days ago: 
https://adsbexchange.com/flight-data-sql-archive/ 
If it comes back up, may be of use, otherwise you may have to rely on international flight records. 
And pros memo attached, as promised â€” again, don't hesitate to be in touch if anything else would be useful, whether in 
the near term or further along in your investigation. Good luck! 
Assistant U.S. Attorney 
Southern District of New York
